{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"1cf11dc11a","title":"关于中苏关系的言论","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"1985b91b7e","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":18,"articleId":"1cf11dc11a"}],"tags":[{"id":"0b6d8a885e","name":"革命委员会","type":"主题/事件"},{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"add118b04e","name":"中国国民党革命委员会"},{"id":"eb0411749e","name":"龙云"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"a7cf46a6c9","type":"title","text":"关于中苏关系的言论","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cf11dc11a"},{"id":"28c9685b8a","type":"authors","text":"中国国民党革命委员会龙云","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cf11dc11a"},{"id":"e16cea256d","type":"subtitle","text":"（龙云：中国国民党革命委员会副主席。以下为六月十八日在民革中央小组扩大会议上揭发的龙云言论）","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cf11dc11a"},{"id":"b8da2d022f","type":"paragraph","text":"(一)抗美援朝战争的经费，全部由中国负担，不合理。","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cf11dc11a"},{"id":"ba3cb657a8","type":"paragraph","text":"(二)第一、第二两次世界大战中，美国借款给盟国，又实施租借法案，后来他们有的赖了债，有的美国不要他们还了。苏联对我国借款，十几年都还不清，还要付利息。中国为社会主义而战，结果如此。","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cf11dc11a"},{"id":"7066343997","type":"paragraph","text":"(三)苏军解放我国东北时，拆走了工厂中的一些机器，有无代价？偿还不偿还？","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cf11dc11a"},{"id":"904cb4e1ec","type":"paragraph","text":"(四)我国援外预算太大，主张抓紧压缩对外的援助。（见六月十九日北京日报）","index":6,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cf11dc11a"},{"id":"9b10faa5ca","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：《提高警惕 粉碎右派阴谋》（1957年6月）。","index":7,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cf11dc11a"}],"page":{"id":"5f2527ad2a","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"1cf11dc11a","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}